flowchart TD
    subgraph Ingestion Pipeline
        A[Upload Document] --> B{Extract Text}
        B --> C[Chunk Text]
        C --> D[(Embed with Gemini)]
        D --> E[Store in pgvector]
    end

    subgraph Query Pipeline
        F[User Query] --> G[(Embed Question with Gemini)]
        G --> H{Vector Search (top-5) in pgvector}
        H --> I[Retrieved Context Chunks]
        I --> J[Send to Gemini with Query + Context]
        J --> K[Return Answer]
    end

    E -- Data Available For --> H